This paper discusses privacy in time series applications, which involves data security and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also discusses differential privacy, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with databases, which is a topic in cs.DB (Databases). The paper also discusses information theory, which is a topic in cs.IT (Information Theory). Finally, the paper discusses privacy in the context of mobile devices and the internet of things, which falls under the category of cs.CY (Computers and Society).
